    - Choose k-2 intermediate vertices from n-2: C(n-2, k-2)
    - Arrange them in order: (k-2)!
    - Distribute weight m among k-1 edges: C(m-1, k-2) stars and bars
    - Form tree structure: n^(n-k-1) * k (Cayley variant)
